{"id": 227, "genre": 1000, "title": "胖是什么感觉？", "description": "一把辛酸泪，很苦的那种。", "record_count": 4720, "comment_count": 80, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201606071942445RYVaOlIrePoCX4u.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-01-16T09:23:24Z", "questions": [{"id": 173, "title": "胖是什么感觉？", "content": "胖是什么感觉", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 1471, "content": "进电梯人再少都担心过载", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192716wSZTURidNV2hnqLx.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1472, "content": "走路多了分分钟进入夏季", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192716bGo176c9LPaQiKUw.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1473, "content": "听“你胖了”和“你瘦了”都觉得是在骂人", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192716cDx3q72UPMTmeiWy.jpeg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1474, "content": "人生还有一种希望：“我瘦下来就会美了”", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192716Z23d7LBokEJRmuG6.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1475, "content": "看到“均码”就能省钱", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192716oVMEd3jY91xtKkbD.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1476, "content": "打三个字都累喘了", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192717lLPIwseqm6QTaCnc.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1477, "content": "啊呀，我又重了，是因为我头发长了吗", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192717cMbJHwtPR9nsz6Zl.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1478, "content": "“好可爱！”", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192717wQ6WkpgaI2N0xGqf.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}